node.text: Imagining what could happen on the lot next to where we are staying in Wrightsville Beach.  We went to Rosemary Beach recently so I have this Cape Dutch style on my mind. Something along these lines would work beautifully on Wrightsville.  This isn’t an actual job.  Just daydreaming on the porch.  #frazierhomedesign #sketching #homedesigner

node.text: Imagining what could happen on the lot next to where we are staying in Wrightsville Beach.  We went to Rosemary Beach recently so I have this Cape Dutch style on my mind. Something along these lines would work beautifully on Wrightsville.  This isn’t an actual job.  Just daydreaming on the porch.  #frazierhomedesign #sketching #homedesigner

node.text: Several of us from @frazierhomedesign went on a site visit to what will be an exclusive 31 lot @loydbuilders neighborhood in North Raleigh!  From 2 mil and up, all built by @loydbuilders and all of them drawn by @frazierhomedesign .  On-site sales by @cvrealtygroup .  We are thrilled to be a part of this team!  The official release will be coming soon!  #luxuryrealestate #architecture #neighborhood
